cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.NA. 

The paper deals with control and estimation of a swarm of robots, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA). The use of diffusion, advection, and reaction as independent control inputs suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of Robotics (cs.RO) or Systems and Control (cs.SY). The analysis of the diffusion-based control strategy using operator semigroup-theoretic arguments suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of Dynamical Systems (cs.DS) or Numerical Analysis (cs.NA).
